<h1><span id="Ruy_Lopez_Open_Defence">Ruy Lopez Open Defence</span></h1>
<p>Black is temporarily two pawns up, but there is a loose knight sitting on an open file leading straight to her king. Why not attack it with 7. Re1?
</p><p>7. c3 is just getting silly. Black will be two clear pawns up and as in the Danish Gambit, she can give one pawn back and run off with the other.
</p>
